{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":16778,"createTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","topicId":null,"tagId":1105,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":5,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">男患，</span>30岁，近30天来右膝关节、足跟部疼痛。既往夜间腰背痛病史。查体：右膝关节肿胀压痛、浮髌试验为阳性，骶髂关节压痛、“4”字试验阳性，足跟部肿胀压痛明显。化验结果提示RF、抗CCP抗体（-），HLA-B27（+）。骶髂关节X线片显示双侧髂骨边缘虫蚀样破坏。治疗宜选择</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">押题点：强直性脊柱炎的治疗。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">解析：患者腰背、膝关节、足跟疼痛，活动受限，</span>HLA-B27（+）、结合骶髂关节X线检查，考虑强直性脊柱炎。非甾体抗炎药(NSAIDs)和抗TNF拮抗剂是治疗AS病人的一线用药。对外周关节受累病人，需使用一种DMARDs药物规律治疗，优选柳氮磺吡啶。对急性眼葡萄膜炎、肌肉关节的炎症可考虑局部直接注射糖皮质激素。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强直性脊柱炎</span>=腰背痛或四肢大关节痛+HLA-B27（+）</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":78044,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","updateTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","isTrue":false,"questionId":16778,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">碳酸氢钠</span>+苯溴马龙</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":78045,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","updateTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","isTrue":true,"questionId":16778,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柳氮磺吡啶</span>+关节内注射倍他米松</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":78046,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","updateTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","isTrue":false,"questionId":16778,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">氨基葡萄糖</span>+双醋瑞因</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":78047,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","updateTime":"2019-07-31 15:51:16","isTrue":false,"questionId":16778,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"