yle=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">解析：系统性红斑狼疮是自身免疫性疾病，表现为多器官受累，如骨关节炎、肾脏、血液系统等，且血抗核抗体阳性，补体</span>C3下降，故考虑最可能为SLE。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统性红斑狼疮</span>=蝶形红斑+光过敏+口腔溃疡+关节炎+ 浆膜炎+白细胞减少等+抗核抗体阳性</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":77764,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":16722,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">类风湿关节炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77765,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":16722,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">骨关节炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77766,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","isTrue":true,"questionId":16722,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统性红斑狼疮</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77767,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":16722,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原发性干燥综合征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77768,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:37:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":16722,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统性血管炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1358,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 16:36:37","updateTime":"2019-06-09 16:36:37","name":"风湿A2","questionCnt":5,"tagTypeId":56},{"id":1105,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 14:25:55","updateTime":"2019-06-09 14:25:55","name":"风湿A2","questionCnt":5,"tagTypeId":51}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":16721,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","topicId":null,"tagId":1105,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">女，</span>28岁，习惯性流产4年，2年前间断面部红斑伴低热。实验室检查：血小板减少、抗核抗体（+），抗心磷脂抗体（+）。右下肢肿胀伴疼痛，有色素沉着。考虑合并的疾病是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">押题点：抗磷脂综合征的临床表现。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">解析：抗磷脂综合征（</span>APS）为一种以反复动脉或者静脉血栓、病态妊娠和抗磷脂抗体（APL）持续阳性的疾患。抗磷脂综合症（APS）可以出现在SLE的活动期，其临床表现为动脉和（或）静脉栓塞形成，习惯性自发性流产，血小板减少，实验室检查抗磷脂抗体阳性。根据患者临床表现和实验室检查结果诊断为APS。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"></span></p><table cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-style: solid;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">妊娠期高血压疾病</span></p></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">主要表现为妊娠期血压增高+抽搐，且既往无高血压病史</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-style: solid;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">干燥综合征</span></p></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">可见唾液腺和泪腺功能不全</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-style: solid;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">弥散性血管内凝血</span></p></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">主要表现为全身血管弥散性血管内凝血，不单局限于下肢</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-style: solid;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">血管闭塞性脉管炎</span></p></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">好发于男性青壮年，与吸烟相关，起病隐匿，进展缓慢。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":77759,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","isTrue":false,"questionId":16721,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">妊娠期高血压疾病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77760,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","isTrue":false,"questionId":16721,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">干燥综合征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77761,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","isTrue":false,"questionId":16721,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弥散性血管内凝血</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77762,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","isTrue":true,"questionId":16721,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">抗磷脂综合征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":77763,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","updateTime":"2019-07-31 14:36:00","isTrue":false,"questionId":16721,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">血管闭塞性脉管炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1358,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 16:36:37","updateTime":"2019-06-09 16:36:37","name":"风湿A2","questionCnt":5,"tagTypeId"